# PROJECT_LOG — Forge cycles (this repository only)

All **cycle numbers**, **velocity reports**, **commit counts toward Auditor**, and **Pattern Distillation** cadences are **per this git repository**. Do not merge logs across projects.

## Operational counters (per repo)

- **Cycle number:** increment in each `## Cycle N` heading below; used for velocity blocks (every 5 cycles) and Pattern Distillation (every 10 cycles).
- **Commits since last audit:** maintain in the latest velocity report or a one-line state note at top; trigger **Auditor** after every **5 commits** (see `CLAUDE.md`).
- **Stagnation:** computed from **this file’s** last three Velocity Reports only.

